<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>7天居家效率手册</title>    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: #f0f2f5;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 24px 16px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 880px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        /* 封面区 */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 48px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .hero .price {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }
        .hero .old-price {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-left: 12px;
        }
        .btn-buy {
            background: #ff9800;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.1s, background 0.2s;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .btn-buy:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
        }
        /* 内容区块 */
        .section {
            padding: 32px 28px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
            display: inline-block;
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
            padding-left: 16px;
        }
        .chapters {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .chapters li {
            background: #f8fafc;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .chapter-num {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .faq {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            margin: 16px 0;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .faq strong {
            color: #334155;
        }
        /* 弹窗样式 */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .modal-content {
            background: white;
            max-width: 360px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 30px 20px 25px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.2s ease;
        }
        .modal-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .modal-content img {
            width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 15px auto;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .close-btn {
            background: #e2e8f0;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            background: #fef9e3;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .section { padding: 24px 20px; }
            .chapters li { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>📘 宅家高效 · 7天实战手册</h1>
        <p>不靠意志力，在家也能进入心流状态</p>
        <div class="price">
            ¥9.90
            <span class="old-price">¥49.00</span>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-buy" onclick="openQR()">📥 立即获取电子书</button>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; opacity: 0.9;">✔️ PDF格式，手机/电脑都可阅读 ✔️ 30天无理由退款</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>📖 目录预览</h2>
        <ul class="chapters">
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D1</span> 重塑你的工作环境 —— 三区分流</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D2</span> 识别你的效率峰值 —— 什么时候工作最投入？</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D3</span> 吃掉那只青蛙 —— 攻克最难任务</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D4</span> 番茄工作法实操 —— 从25分钟开始</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D5</span> 数字极简编码 —— 给手机和大脑减负</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D6</span> 精力管理而非时间管理 —— 学会主动休息</li>
            <li><span class="chapter-num">D7</span> 建立你的“不完美”系统 —— 长期自律的秘密</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="text-align:center; color:#667eea; margin-top:20px;">📄 共 58 页，约 25,000 字，PDF 格式</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>✍️ 关于作者</h2>
        <p>一位从事虚拟现实与自然艺术的普通人。经过两年亲身实践，总结出这套不依赖意志力的居家工作方法。相信每个人都能找到属于自己的高效节奏。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>❓ 常见问题</h2>
        <div class="faq"><strong>Q：这本书适合什么样的人？</strong><br>A：只要你经常在家办公或学习，容易被分心困扰，这本书就适合你。不需要任何基础。</div>
        <div class="faq"><strong>Q：购买后如何收到电子书？</strong><br>A：支付成功后，系统会将 PDF 电子书发送到您的邮箱。如果没有收到，请检查垃圾邮件箱或联系我们。</div>
        <div class="faq"><strong>Q：可以退款吗？</strong><br>A：当然可以！购买后 30 天内，如果你觉得没有收获，全额退款，无需理由。</div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 我的电子书小铺 · Powered by GitHub Pages
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 支付弹窗 -->
<div id="qrModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <h3>💰 扫码支付 ¥9.90</h3>
        <p style="color:#666;">支持支付宝 / 微信 / 云闪付</p>
        <!-- ⚠️ 重要：把下面的图片链接换成你自己的收款二维码图片地址 -->
        < img src="mmexport1711982891801.jpg" alt="收款二维码" id="qrcodeImg">
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">支付后请截图并发送到邮箱 📧 hi@example.com ，我们将在5分钟内发送PDF</p>
        <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeQR()">关闭</button>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    function openQR() {
        document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'flex';
    }
    function closeQR() {
        document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'none';
    }
    window.onclick = function(event) {
        var modal = document.getElementById('qrModal');
        if (event.target === modal) {
            modal.style.display = 'none';
        }
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
